WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.498
The most powerful financial incentive, however, lies in pre-existing cloud

00:00:04.498 --> 00:00:08.997
contracts. If a scaled customer has signed an Enterprise Discount

00:00:08.997 --> 00:00:13.495
Plan or Private Pricing Agreement, then purchasing AppsFlyer through the

00:00:13.495 --> 00:00:17.993
marketplace allows them to retire up to twenty-five percent of

00:00:17.993 --> 00:00:22.491
those massive, committed cloud spends. This causal mechanism brilliantly turns

00:00:22.491 --> 00:00:26.990
historic internal objectors, such as highly rigid procurement and conservative

00:00:26.990 --> 00:00:31.488
finance departments, into enthusiastic supporters.
